title: How much of a plane spotter are you?
text: Fancy yourself an aviation expert? Find out just how many aircraft models you can recognise by taking our quiz. Once you're done, try our quizzes on Commonwealth flags , cities from the sky , island outlines , British seaside resorts , weird driving laws , airport codes , world flags and obscure capital cities .
